name: UniverseStable
description:
Welcome to UniverseStable

This model is mainly designed for artistic portraits and full-length photos. Photorealistic landscapes, monsters and more, this model is versatile for any request.

Recommend: DPM++2M SDE Karras, Clip skip 1 Sampler, Steps: 25-35, CFG scale: 5-7

  • My Universal Style: "photo RAW,({prompt}), masterpiece, award winning photography, lighting, perfect composition, high detail, hyper realistic,dramatic lighting, epic"

    Negative: "low quality,medium quality, 3d,frame,bw,watermark,logo,((letters)),paint,draw,(text),(worst quality:2), (low quality:2), (normal quality:2), lowres, bad anatomy, bad hands, normal quality, ((monochrome)), ((grayscale))"

A merge model from a dozen diverse models, with the expectation of high-quality and interesting generations.

I will be glad and grateful for the placement of generations using this model.
